Package: rcicero
Title: This package is a wrapper for the Cicero API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("David", "Ranzolin", email = "daranzolin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package makes getting data from the Cicero API easier for
    useRs. The objects returned by its functions are admittedly messy data frames,
    and some of the data may require unnesting, but it includes everything available
    from Cicero.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.2.2)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Imports: httr,
    jsonlite,
    tidyjson,
    dplyr,
    magrittr
URL: https://github.com/daranzolin/rcicero
BugReports: https://github.com/daranzolin/rcicero/issues
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
